title: Godsmack - An Evening with Godsmack - DVD
description:
An Evening with Godsmack DVD that was included in the 2007 release of "Good Times, Bad Times; 10 Years of Godsmack". It's in 5.1 channel surround sound. Watch with VLC media player or burn the files to a dvd and get ready to rock. It's a great acoustic set recorded at the House of Blues in Las Vegas.
